@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nywlut(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.abs(0.91) - ((v0 + 0.04 + v0 + 0.12) - 0.28))
    v2 = 0.25
    v0 = ((0.13 - wp.abs(tmp + 0.98)) + (wp.abs(tmp + 0.28) + 0.68))
    v1 = (v0 * wp.exp((tmp + 0.39 + v2 + 0.69)))
    v2 = wp.exp((0.86 + (tmp + 0.70 / v2 + 0.84)))
    data[tid] = v0
